TEXT.TITLE: TABUCHI ELECTRIC ISSUES 30 MLN SWISS FRANC NOTES
TEXT.BODY: Tabuchi Electric Co is launching 30 mln Swiss francs of five-year straight notes with a 4-3/4 pct coupon and par issue price, lead mananger Swiss Bank Corp said. Payment is due April 22. REUTER
